text:
INGREDIENTS:
Meatloaf;
Chop an onion (brunoise)
1 egg
(Some) breadcrumbs
Just as much milk as it can absorb
(1 kg) ground meat
Salt and pepper
Knead gently

2 tablespoons of brown sugar
2 tablespoons of (yellow) mustard
(Some) ketchup
Pour all over the meatloaf
190¬∞C, 60-90 mins

Mashed potatoes;
Red potatoes*
Butter
Milk
Salt
Pepper
(No measure)
*Russets and Yellow Potatoes (high-starch potatoes) are better than red potatoes for mashing

Broccoli;
Broccoli

Washing vegetables and your hands (after touching raw meat) can be healthier. And, yes Chef, i want to have your chewed shonion.
